name: Kehadiran (The Presence)
description:
The story of a man who is guarding the security of the neighborhood at a guard post at night. Suddenly he was approached by something saying a mysterious request.

A CGA pixel art short movie (Indonesian language) by Bujubuneng.

Taken from a comic I made, entitled: 
"Cyborg Warrior - Awakening of Cyborg Lady Satan"
